	<dl>
	<dt>Not voting is better than Spoiling....

...</dt>
	<dd><p>Not voting is better than Spoiling....</p> <p>Have a look at the media now.  Do you see a count of spoiled ballots anywhere?  Any mention of it at all?  No, you don't.  Those who chose to vote for "none of the above" have had their vote ignored again.</p> <p>Next time you'll know better and know not to vote at all.</p>
	<small>
	written 6th May 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1875">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=1875">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

